{"tid":941516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本自民黨通過將「出雲」號航母化　列入新防衛大綱","createTime":"2018-12-15T00:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T00:22:37.000Z","uid":8543,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a06df9c82d5679182cd578eb354141f4189b446e","tid":941516,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"執政自民黨周三召開國防小組和安全保障調查會聯席會議，會上通過將護衛艦「出雲號」航母化計劃，列入新《防衛計劃大綱》專守防衛範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n自民黨周四（13日）將就文件草案與執政聯盟公明黨達成正式協議。<br />\n<br />\n當局曾討論，「出雲號」的目標是要搭載並運用可短距離起飛及垂直着陸的F-35B隱形戰機。惟草案文件未有列明改後的「出雲號」會否常態化搭載F-35B戰機。<br />\n<br />\n有意見認為，將「出雲」號航母化是為應對中國頻繁的海洋活動，加強日本防衛能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/270492/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%87%AA%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%87-%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%B2-%E8%99%9F%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E5%8C%96-%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B0%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F270492%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B0%2587-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%259B%25B2-%25E8%2599%259F%25E8%2588%25AA%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%258C%2596-%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25B6%25B1&d=K%2FtronHRi6BLACeVraY2JPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=18f478f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/270492/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%87%AA%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%87-%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%B2-%E8%99%9F%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E5%8C%96-%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B0%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%B1</a>"}]}